room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
room_description: After renting a cabin in the woods to escape city life, you and your fellow adventurers were in the middle of a hike and stumbled upon a quickly moving forest fire. Everyone raced back to the cabin to gather their belongings before vacating the forest... only to become trapped in the cabin. You have 1 hour to escape the cabin and out run the fire.
